cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to modify projector input images. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes it likely to belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with the appearance of projection surfaces. Finally, the paper involves multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with the compensation of projector images.
